text.paragraph:
When Cefazolin for Injection is administered to patients with low urinary output because of impaired renal function, lower daily dosage is required (see 
                              DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION
                           ).

As with other β-lactam antibiotics, seizures may occur if inappropriately high doses are administered to patients with impaired renal function (see 
                              DOSAGE AND ADMINISTRATION
                           ).
